11:11.880 --> 11:15.520
As a person with a spinal cord injury,
I, like so many others,

11:15.600 --> 11:19.240
have experienced the realities
of trying to attain medical care

11:19.320 --> 11:22.760
while confronting the seismic barriers
that still exist

11:22.760 --> 11:27.120
despite the over 30 years
since the Americans with Disabilities Act

11:27.200 --> 11:29.040
became law,

11:29.040 --> 11:32.840
so many of us have stories to tell.

