Carrier Access Act,

01:43:00.040 --> 01:43:05.320
the Americans with Disabilities Act,
Section 504 of the Rehabilitation Act,

01:43:05.400 --> 01:43:09.120
Section 508 and Section 503.

01:43:09.200 --> 01:43:11.200
We also wanted to advance

01:43:11.200 --> 01:43:16.000
diversity, equality, inclusion,
and accessibility of the DOT.

01:43:16.040 --> 01:43:17.760
workforce.

01:43:17.760 --> 01:43:20.760
We wanted to address gaps in data,

01:43:20.960 --> 01:43:23.480
on people with disabilities in transportation.

01:43:23.480 --> 01:43:27.280
There is a huge lack of data
in transportation

01:43:27.280 --> 01:43:31.920
on people with disabilities specifically.

01:43:32.000 --> 01:43:35.520
And then we also wanted to make sure
that all DOT

01:43:35.560 --> 01:43:40.600
meetings were fully accessible to people with disabilities.

