on accessible accessible lavatories.

01:45:57.800 --> 01:46:01.560
There's a number of things
that are going to be required in the next

01:46:01.640 --> 01:46:04.920
three years,
which one is to make the interior of the

01:46:05.000 --> 01:46:08.560
of the bathrooms on single aisle
aircraft more accessible.

01:46:08.560 --> 01:46:13.440
by providing some of the features that have to now be  accessible,

01:46:13.520 --> 01:46:16.200
like are grab bars,

01:46:16.200 --> 01:46:19.840
accessible water faucets, that kind of stuff.

01:46:19.920 --> 01:46:23.560
