02:10:45.400 --> 02:10:49.400
So to the regulation
that I was just mentioning

02:10:49.480 --> 02:10:54.480
require that if a private entity
that's primarily engaged in the business

02:10:54.480 --> 02:11:00.600
of transporting people operates
a fixed route transportation service

02:11:00.680 --> 02:11:05.560
and purchases or releases a new vehicle
other than an automobile or van

02:11:05.560 --> 02:11:09.760
with a seating capacity of less than eight
passengers, including the driver,

02:11:09.840 --> 02:11:14.440
that vehicle must be readily accessible
to and usable by individuals

02:11:14.440 --> 02:11:18.920
with disabilities,
including individuals who use wheelchairs

02:11:19.000 --> 02:11:21.000
if it's not a fixed route system,

02:11:21.000 --> 02:11:24.880
but rather a demand responsive system

02:11:24.960 --> 02:11:29.160
and the transportation and the entity is

02:11:29.160 --> 02:11:33.320
primarily engaged
in the business of transporting people

02:11:33.400 --> 02:11:35.520
and it purchases or releases

02:11:35.520 --> 02:11:40.040
a new vehicle other than an automobile
or van with a seating capacity

02:11:40.040 --> 02:11:43.520
of less than eight passengers,
including the driver.

02:11:43.600 --> 02:11:46.880
That vehicle must be readily accessible
to and usable by

02:11:46.960 --> 02:11:51.400
individuals with disabilities,
including individuals who use wheelchairs

02:11:51.480 --> 02:11:55.520
unless the system,
when viewed in its entirety,

02:11:55.600 --> 02:12:00.640
meets the standard
for what we call equivalent service.

02:12:00.720 --> 02:12:04.000
The regulations and the law
explain equivalent service

02:12:04.000 --> 02:12:08.520
as a level of service to individuals
with disabilities, equivalent

02:12:08.520 --> 02:12:12.280
to the level of service
provided to the general public.

02:12:12.360 --> 02:12:16.120
And that relates to things
like response time

02:12:16.200 --> 02:12:21.120
fares, geographic area of service, hours
and days of service,

02:12:21.200 --> 02:12:24.000
availability of information, reservation

02:12:24.000 --> 02:12:27.000
capability, any constraints on capacity

02:12:27.080 --> 02:12:32.440
or service availability
or restrictions based on trip purpose.

02:12:32.520 --> 02:12:34.720
So I know I just

02:12:34.720 --> 02:12:38.600
