of disability discrimination

02:15:38.560 --> 02:15:42.880
to pay tens of thousands of dollars
to individuals who had been aggrieved

02:15:42.880 --> 02:15:46.440
and complained to United States
about their mistreatment

02:15:46.680 --> 02:15:50.920
and to pay the United States a civil penalty.

02:15:51.000 --> 02:15:51.960
Under

02:15:51.960 --> 02:15:55.120
that settlement agreement, not investigate
