to board a vehicle.

02:17:15.600 --> 02:17:20.080
than Uber was giving them, which was 2
minutes before the fee would be imposed.

02:17:20.160 --> 02:17:24.920
So the United States sued Uber as
a private entity, primarily engaged

02:17:24.920 --> 02:17:29.040
in the business of transporting people
under the ADA

02:17:29.120 --> 02:17:31.920
for charging illegal fees,

02:17:31.920 --> 02:17:36.560
for denying adequate boarding time,
which is something the ADA requires,

02:17:36.640 --> 02:17:39.680
