for individuals

02:17:57.480 --> 02:18:00.920
who don't opt in to that program
and are charged with time fees

02:18:00.920 --> 02:18:06.120
because of disability,
Uber agrees to promptly refund them,

02:18:06.200 --> 02:18:08.280
and it

02:18:08.280 --> 02:18:13.120
