to train its staff on the new policy.

02:18:13.200 --> 02:18:16.200
It also agreed to provide payment

02:18:16.200 --> 02:18:19.440
to over 65,000 individuals
who had been charged

02:18:19.440 --> 02:18:22.680
wait time fees likely due to disability, over

02:18:22.680 --> 02:18:27.320
$2 million to individuals
who had complained

02:18:27.560 --> 02:18:30.760
to the United States or Uber,
and to pay the United States

02:18:30.840 --> 02:18:34.920
a civil penalty under a two year
settlement agreement.

